Usage: merge_clock_cells [-help] [ -only_clock_logics  | -only_clock_gates  ] [ -only_clock_logics  | -only_above_flops  ]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-only_above_flops      # Only attempt to merge clock gates that drive just
                       # flops. (bool, optional)
-only_clock_gates      # Only clock gates. Does not merge clock logics.
                       # (bool, optional)
-only_clock_logics     # Only merge clock logics. Does not merge clock gates.
                       # (bool, optional)